{"tid":210522,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"着短裙，勁無奈！","createTime":"2017-04-21T04:13:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-22T11:04:48.000Z","uid":76855,"like":5,"dislike":480,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a40224d75f79cd6ef5e129fb19dae4e203ee05c4","tid":210522,"uid":76855,"like":2,"dislike":33,"score":-31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T04:13:28.000Z","msg":"岩先行過荃灣海霸街附近整緊個條路<br />\n<br />\n有幾個地盤老係到做野<br />\n<br />\n咁我係佢地隔離行過，我今日着左條連身短裙，都幾短下，吾過室頭，出邊透透地，黑色，但入邊有條白色底裙係吾透嘅！<br />\n<br />\n之後有個地盤老mou低做緊野，但佢冇留意我，另一個見到我行緊過來即刻夾硬扭mou低個個野個頭過來我哩邊，做成裝我裙底嘅姿勢<br />\n<br />\nmou低個個野知道俾人整估，就鬧佢同事，＂x你老x，衰左坐十年嫁＂咁！<br />\n<br />\n嬲我又吾係好嬲，因為佢裝吾到，但我當時真係好無奈，吾知俾咩反應佢好<br />\n<br />\n唯有扮吾知，聽吾到，行過就算！！個兩個野幾後生添，不過d行為眞係灰所！！"},{"pid":"08edf8478fc786ab81bbafa893bc191b6b06d0af","tid":210522,"uid":14912,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T04:15:53.000Z","msg":"好彩冇比佢睇蝕咋!😊<br />\n著短裙真係要打足底，提防走光！"},{"pid":"13a9fb4a7980b56ff141e36072d84499416b3a15","tid":210522,"uid":70361,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T04:46:13.000Z","msg":"block都block唔撚切"},{"pid":"dc1df19d1ff1d2810f553c23c4f12dc57b5b2e29","tid":210522,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T05:02:34.000Z","msg":"仆街唔小心click錯正評 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dce395d9f67a2bff28b335f87d7c2915cec1e12","tid":210522,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T05:04:42.000Z","msg":"圖呢🤤🤤"},{"pid":"3a5488ffed71c722534c5963cd650511571cb67c","tid":210522,"uid":987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T05:05:54.000Z","msg":"吾你老母"},{"pid":"5fedad4c904dccf15cb3f94e018508905b3fc2b1","tid":210522,"uid":97514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T05:15:05.000Z","msg":"On9先著安全褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/nor